    firstAppointment: `Nerve conduction studies, EMG results, and recent metabolic labs (HbA1c, B12, heavy metals, inflammatory markers) are all helpful. Describe the pattern and character of your neuropathic symptoms — location, whether it's constant or intermittent, what makes it worse or better.`,
