    howItWorks: `Herbal consultations involve the same Chinese medical diagnostic process as acupuncture — tongue and pulse examination, pattern differentiation, symptom questioning. Based on the diagnosis, Dr. Hendry prescribes a formula (classical, modified classical, or custom composition) and explains what the formula is designed to do, what to expect, and when to return for reassessment.`,
