    firstAppointment: `Inform Dr. Hendry of any cardiovascular conditions, multiple sclerosis, or heat-sensitive neurological conditions. Drink 16–32 oz of water before each infrared sauna session and replenish electrolytes afterward. Avoid sessions immediately before or after vigorous exercise.`,
